abel_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661537655"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5dTQ46jX9NhLEAMaCTEwOTI4NjE0MiC5ysq0BjAAOJwDQB1yCTY2MTUzNzY1NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1721294458.364588", "card_id": "Q_661905943", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "报道称普华永道将裁掉一半在中国的金融审计员工，公司回应称调整是艰难的决定，具体情况如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 17 日，有媒体报道称，普华永道考虑将在中国的金融服务审计员工裁减多达一半。此外，普华永道还在考虑裁掉其他审计团队和非审计业务线约 20% 的员工。 对此，普华永道公关团队表示：「由于外部客观情况的变化，我们根据市场需求相应优化了组织架构。我们一直珍视人才并持续多年大力投资于人才培养，此次调整是艰难的决定。我们正逐步与员工展开充分的沟通，并确保调整方案遵守中国劳动法相关规定。」普华永道将裁掉一半在中国的金融审计员工？回应称，调整是艰难的决定 _ 牛市点线面 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2bb991deccdb4148d574d6744ad6fbd4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661905943"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5dTQ46jX9NhLEAMaCTEwOTM2ODA0MiCqteG0BjAAOJ8BQB5yCTY2MTkwNTk0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1721294458.365318", "card_id": "Q_654929915", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 115}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很多人回到老家里感觉很放松？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "现在生活节奏加快，城镇增多，很多除外打工的人，节假日总是想着回去一趟。 不仅是亲人，看望，有时候也是心灵的放松。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3820e8b9386769cb14e072d0eaa98df4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654929915"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5dTQ46jX9NhLEAMaCTEwNzgxNzY1MiCkuNaxBjAAOMcBQB9yCTY1NDkyOTkxNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1",